# Qualcomm Snapdragon NPU + LiteRT-LM native libraries.
# The .so files (some up to 82 MB) are from the Qualcomm QNN SDK and are
# too large for GitHub. Anyone cloning this repo and wanting to build for
# Snapdragon NPU needs to drop these in app/src/main/jniLibs/arm64-v8a/
# from their own SDK install.
